      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">The World Scrabble Championship is the pinnacle of competitive word gaming — where the planet's most brilliant lexical minds battle over tiles for the ultimate title. Since 1991, this event has crowned champions from across continents, featured unforgettable comebacks, and showcased the game at its highest level. Here's the full story of Scrabble's greatest stage.</p>

